Text: Wells Fargo & Company MN increased its holdings in shares of BlackRock Enhanced Global Dividend Trust by 2.6% in the 2nd quarter. Wells Fargo & Company MN now owns 1,963,293 shares of the financial services provider's stock worth $21,066,000 after buying an additional 48,839 shares during the last quarter.
